Subject: The disk of the server is increasing very quickly
Description:
The disk of the server is increasing very quickly, especially the shadow log section. I have cleaned the shadow log, but it only reduced a little.

Please have remote session to check. Many thanks
What_We_Know__c: Space occupied by shadows and AUdit log backup size
Solution_Comment__c: Cleare older sahdows and recommended the user to download the Audit then delete them.
